ka Amami和其他人所属的765专业人士有关，但DS之后的发展受到限制。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[我试图唱歌]“你好!!”  - 白星[被vα -liv覆盖]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zxBftixd3Gk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>实际上，截至一年前，Vα-LIV偶像候选人的财产也有一首精美的明星歌曲盖，可以说这一点在这一点上得到了暗示。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.7qf7hf17xa6c-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.7qf7hf17xa6c-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.7qf7hf17xa6c-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.7qf7hf17xa6c-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/809e9b9e6657ff304de7ef049e47012f-kix.7qf7hf17xa6c-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> Ishikawa总统的一封信息也随着此隶属关系的宣布而发布。我担心不仅会重新启动三个偶像活动，而且还会重新开始876专业。</p><p> ©toshiyuki kuboka the Idolm@ster <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ＆©Bandai Namco Entertainment Inc.<br /> （参考） <a href="https://twitter.com/valiv_official/status/1774403943122260404" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方X（前Twitter）</a> ，<a href="https://idolmaster-official.jp/news/01_11156" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方新闻</a>，<a href="https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/software/vimj/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">任天堂DS官方页面</a></p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/project-imas-v%ce%b1-liv-876/">偶像大师的开发项目“Vα-LIV（Viirive）”通过了最终考试！附属的“ 876 Pro”是SNS上的一个主题，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura V