从Vtuber集团“ Avatar2.0项目”，Yui Yui，Shia Mizuse离开，继续他的活动作为免费https://www.moguravr.com/avatar2-0-project-yui-sia/MoguLive編集部 Mon, 01 Apr 2024 06:16:39 +0000 VTuberAvatar2.0 Project水瀬しあ結目ユイ https://www.moguravr.com/?p=249076 <p> 4月1日，VTUBER集团“ Avatar2.0项目”宣布Yui Yui和Shia Mizuse将离开。 Shia Minase将继续从5月1日释放，Yui Yui将从4月1日获得免费。现在 […]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/avatar2-0-project-yui-sia/">Vtuber邮政“ Avatar2.0项目”，Yui Yui，Shii Mizuse退休，继续进行免费活动，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p> 4月1日，VTUBER集团“ Avatar2.0项目”宣布<a href="https://twitter.com/musubimeyui" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yui Yui</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/minase_shia" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shia Mizuse</a>将离开。 Shia Minase将继续从5月1日释放，Yui Yui将从4月1日获得免费。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/bb47c2c415466d214309dc326ab809d4-kix.wsshlal4oa5t-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/bb47c2c415466d214309dc326ab809d4-kix.wsshlal4oa5t-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/bb47c2c415466d214309dc326ab809d4-kix.wsshlal4oa5t-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/bb47c2c415466d214309dc326ab809d4-kix.wsshlal4oa5t-300x150.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/bb47c2c415466d214309dc326ab809d4-kix.wsshlal4oa5t-768x384.webp 768w" width="800" height="400" /></a></p><p>离开两个人的原因是与该人协商后下一步的目的。两人发布了有关此离开的公告。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja"> [重要新闻] <a href="https://t.co/WhdWgXcQ8m">pic.twitter.com/whdwgxcq8m</a></p><p> -  Shia Misase <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f3d6.png" alt="🏖" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />五周年释放<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2668.png" alt="♨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> （@minase_shia） <a href="